data.description: Looking for a wooded one acre lot with a gorgeous modern kitchen, real hardwood floors, massive bedrooms, two living rooms, and move-in ready? Here it is! Located at the end of a no outlet street, 81 Centerwood is ready for it’s new owners. The 24’x14’ primary suite includes an ensuite bath, and a large walk in closet. Mechanicals all under 10 years, Carrier HVAC, well insulated, dimensional roof 11 years, and the new above ground pool can stay or go. Home warranty included, VA & FHA buyers welcome - this home is in great shape and it’s perfect for gatherings with family and friends. Washington Township, no city taxes! Centerville schools.
